{"day":13,"topic":{"title":"Use of Let","emoji":"🤝","cefr":"A2","difficulty":"elementary","type":"grammar"},"content":{"explanation":"\n**Let — Permission & Suggestion:**\n\n\"Let\" = होने देना / करने देना / अनुमति देना\n\n**3 Main Uses:**\n\n**Use 1: Permission देना**\nLet + object + base verb\n🇮🇳 मुझे जाने दो।\n🇬🇧 Let me go.\n\n**Use 2: Causative (करवाना)**\n🇮🇳 उसे बोलने दो।\n🇬🇧 Let him speak.\n\n**Use 3: Suggestion (Let's)**\n🇮🇳 चलो खाना खाते हैं।\n🇬🇧 Let's eat. (Let us eat)\n  ","rules":["Let + object (me/him/her/them/us) + base verb (no \"to\")","Let me + verb = मुझे [verb] करने दो","Let him/her + verb = उसे [verb] करने दो","Let's = Let us (suggestion for group)","Negative of Let's: Let's not + verb","Don't let + object + verb = मत करने दो","Formal: Please let me know / Do not let them enter"],"memoryTrick":"**LET = Allow (अनुमति)** — Let me / Let him / Let's — इनके बाद हमेशा base verb (no to, no -ing).","examples":[{"hindi":"मुझे समझाने दो।","english":"Let me explain.","type":"Let me + verb"},{"hindi":"उसे जाने दो।","english":"Let him go.","type":"Let him + verb"},{"hindi":"चलो मिलकर काम करते हैं।","english":"Let's work together.","type":"Let's (suggestion)"},{"hindi":"मुझे एक मिनट दो।","english":"Let me have a minute.","type":"Let me + verb"},{"hindi":"उन्हें अंदर आने दो।","english":"Let them come in.","type":"Let them + verb"},{"hindi":"चलो यह भूल जाते हैं।","english":"Let's forget about it.","type":"Let's + verb"}],"mistakes":[{"wrong":"Let me to go.","correct":"Let me go.","why":"Let के बाद \"to\" नहीं आता"},{"wrong":"Let's to eat.","correct":"Let's eat.","why":"Let's के बाद base verb (no to)"},{"wrong":"Let him going.","correct":"Let him go.","why":"Let + object + base verb (no -ing)"},{"wrong":"Don't lets go.","correct":"Let's not go.","why":"Negative suggestion = Let's not + verb"}],"speakingTips":["Office mein: \"Let me check and get back to you.\"","Friends ke saath: \"Let's go for dinner tonight!\"","Meetings mein: \"Let's start the meeting.\" / \"Let me share my screen.\""]},"vocabulary":[{"id":1,"word":"Allow","hindi":"अनुमति देना","ipa":"","example":"Please allow me to help."},{"id":2,"word":"Permit","hindi":"अनुमति","ipa":"","example":"The boss permitted early leave."},{"id":3,"word":"Enable","hindi":"सक्षम करना","ipa":"","example":"This will enable us to grow."},{"id":4,"word":"Suggest","hindi":"सुझाव देना","ipa":"","example":"I suggest we leave early."},{"id":5,"word":"Propose","hindi":"प्रस्ताव करना","ipa":"","example":"Let's propose a new idea."},{"id":6,"word":"Refuse","hindi":"मना करना","ipa":"","example":"He refused to let me in."},{"id":7,"word":"Grant","hindi":"मंज़ूर करना","ipa":"","example":"The manager granted permission."},{"id":8,"word":"Approve","hindi":"स्वीकृति देना","ipa":"","example":"The plan was approved."}],"practice":[{"id":"d13-001","hindi":"मुझे जाने दो।","english":"Let me go.","alternatives":["let me leave."],"hint":"Let me + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-002","hindi":"उसे बोलने दो।","english":"Let him speak.","alternatives":["let him talk."],"hint":"Let him + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-003","hindi":"उन्हें अंदर आने दो।","english":"Let them come in.","alternatives":["allow them to come in."],"hint":"Let them + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-004","hindi":"मुझे समझाने दो।","english":"Let me explain.","alternatives":["allow me to explain."],"hint":"Let me + explain","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-005","hindi":"उसे अपनी बात कहने दो।","english":"Let her say what she wants.","alternatives":["let her speak."],"hint":"Let her + say/speak","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-006","hindi":"मुझे एक मिनट दो।","english":"Let me have a minute.","alternatives":["give me a minute."],"hint":"Let me have + time","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-007","hindi":"बच्चों को खेलने दो।","english":"Let the children play.","alternatives":["allow the children to play."],"hint":"Let + noun + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-008","hindi":"उसे यह काम करने दो।","english":"Let him do this work.","alternatives":["allow him to do this work."],"hint":"Let him + do","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-009","hindi":"मुझे अपना काम करने दो।","english":"Let me do my work.","alternatives":["allow me to do my work."],"hint":"Let me + do my work","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-010","hindi":"उसे अपनी मनपसंद चीज़ चुनने दो।","english":"Let her choose what she likes.","alternatives":["let her pick what she wants."],"hint":"Let her + choose","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-011","hindi":"कुत्ते को बाहर जाने दो।","english":"Let the dog go outside.","alternatives":["allow the dog to go out."],"hint":"Let the + noun + verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-012","hindi":"उन्हें जवाब देने दो।","english":"Let them answer.","alternatives":["allow them to respond."],"hint":"Let them + answer","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-013","hindi":"मुझे तुम्हारी मदद करने दो।","english":"Let me help you.","alternatives":["allow me to help you."],"hint":"Let me + help","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-014","hindi":"उसे खुद तय करने दो।","english":"Let him decide for himself.","alternatives":["allow him to decide."],"hint":"Let him + decide","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-015","hindi":"मुझे देखने दो।","english":"Let me see.","alternatives":["allow me to look."],"hint":"Let me + see","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-016","hindi":"उसे गाने दो।","english":"Let her sing.","alternatives":["allow her to sing."],"hint":"Let her + sing","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-017","hindi":"हमें कोशिश करने दो।","english":"Let us try.","alternatives":["let's try."],"hint":"Let us + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-018","hindi":"उन्हें शांति से रहने दो।","english":"Let them be in peace.","alternatives":["let them live in peace."],"hint":"Let them + be","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-019","hindi":"मुझे सोचने दो।","english":"Let me think.","alternatives":["give me a moment to think."],"hint":"Let me + think","explanation":""},{"id":"d13-020","hindi":"बारिश आने दो।","english":"Let it rain.","alternatives":["allow it to rain."],"hint":"Le